metadata.name: REKT
metadata.description:
GM to everyone trying to change their life with NFTs!

Many are going to make it. Nevertheless, some seek help. 

FOMO, anxiety, coping with loss and other issues put a lot of pressure on our mental health.

The space has been good to me and I want to give something back. I am an IRL psychotherapist and I can help.

This is my genesis piece. Itâ€™s my first move! 

My mission is to link mental health courses to the blockchain.

This piece is for all the rektgals and rektguys. Community above all. Together we will grow.
